As far as I understand the `plan.xml` variables are only used inside the `plan.xml` file. You need to put values somewhere else to access them. The simplest way would be the servlet context parameter in `web.xml`. For example:

**web.xml**

    &lt;?xml version=&quot;1.0&quot; encoding=&quot;UTF-8&quot;?&gt;
    &lt;web-app version=&quot;2.5&quot; xmlns=&quot;http://java.sun.com/xml/ns/javaee&quot;     xmlns:xsi=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance&quot;     xsi:schemaLocation=&quot;http://java.sun.com/xml/ns/javaee http://java.sun.com/xml/ns/javaee/web-app_2_5.xsd&quot;&gt;
     ...
     &lt;context-param&gt;
        &lt;param-name&gt;spring.profiles.active&lt;/param-name&gt;
        &lt;param-value&gt;inject_value_here&lt;/param-value&gt;
      &lt;/context-param&gt;
      ...
    &lt;/web-app&gt;

**plan.xml**

    &lt;?xml version=&#39;1.0&#39; encoding=&#39;UTF-8&#39;?&gt;
    &lt;deployment-plan xmlns=&quot;http://xmlns.oracle.com/weblogic/deployment-plan&quot;xmlns:xsi=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance&quot; xsi:schemaLocation=&quot;http://xmlns.oracle.com/weblogic/deployment-plan http://xmlns.oracle.com/weblogic/deployment-plan/1.0/deployment-plan.xsd&quot; global-variables=&quot;true&quot;&gt;
      &lt;application-name&gt;appname&lt;/application-name&gt;
      &lt;variable-definition&gt;
        &lt;variable&gt;
          &lt;name&gt;springProfilesActive&lt;/name&gt;
          &lt;value&gt;dev&lt;/value&gt;
        &lt;/variable&gt;
      &lt;/variable-definition&gt;
      &lt;module-override&gt;
        &lt;module-name&gt;appname.war&lt;/module-name&gt;
        &lt;module-type&gt;war&lt;/module-type&gt;
        &lt;module-descriptor external=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
          &lt;root-element&gt;web-app&lt;/root-element&gt;
          &lt;uri&gt;WEB-INF/web.xml&lt;/uri&gt;
          &lt;variable-assignment&gt;
             &lt;name&gt;springProfilesActive&lt;/name&gt;
             &lt;xpath&gt;/web-app/context-param/[param-name=&quot;spring.profiles.active&quot;]/param-value&lt;/xpath&gt;
             &lt;origin&gt;planbased&lt;/origin&gt;
          &lt;/variable-assignment&gt;
        &lt;/module-descriptor&gt;
      &lt;/module-override&gt;
    &lt;/deployment-plan&gt;

You can access this context parameter with `ServletContext.getInitParameter`.

More information and examples:
