                                    &lt;/manifestEntries&gt;
                                &lt;/transformer&gt;
                            &lt;/transformers&gt;
                        &lt;/configuration&gt;
                    &lt;/execution&gt;
                &lt;/executions&gt;
            &lt;/plugin&gt;

Of course, you should use your own Shade plugin version number

