Thus, **surprisingly** your test is not even being run with JUnit. Instead, it is being run with Maven Surefire&#39;s support for what they call [POJO Tests](http://maven.apache.org/surefire/maven-surefire-plugin/examples/pojo-test.html).

Adding the following to your `pom.xml` should solve the problem.

